Saya lapar, jadi saya mendapat sup ekor lembu.

449
00:26:50,567 --> 00:26:52,193
Saya sangat kenyang.

450
00:26:52,194 --> 00:26:53,569
itu bagus.

451
00:26:53,570 --> 00:26:54,947
Hei, Hayeong.

452
00:26:55,739 --> 00:26:59,992
